   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-noquest" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>
I still can't trace the whereabouts of the people who went to the Spirit's Grave.<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Need to complete the sub-quest, Spirit's Treasure)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting" image="QW_37.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-a" mid="7" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>No, there were no traces of any people.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>When you were at the <FONT color=#a82424>Spirit's Grave</FONT>, did you find any traces of people?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-b" mid="9" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>Hmm, everyone who went there must have really disappeared. What a pity. What would I tell <FONT color=#a94407>Jeffery's mother</FONT>....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-c" mid="11" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>Among the adventurers who went to the <FONT color=#a82424>Spirit's Grave</FONT>, there was a kid called <FONT color=#a94407>Jeffery</FONT>. He was a good kid who took care of his mother in a poor environment.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-d" mid="13" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>He thought he could make his mother live a better life if he found the <FONT color=#a94407>Spirit's Treasure</FONT> and went to the <FONT color=#a82424>Spirit's Grave</FONT>. As you well know, no one has returned from that place.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-d" image="QW_37.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-e" mid="15" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(what to do)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR><FONT color=#a94407>Jeffery's mother</FONT> wants to know whether her son is alive. So, I was wondering if you could go to the <FONT color=#a82424>Spirit's Grave</FONT> and find his belongings to find a clue to where he went. Can you help?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-accepting-acceptted" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>Accept Quest</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Search for Missing People$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-1" image="QW_37.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>Thank you. Then go to the <FONT color=#a82424>Spirit's Grave</FONT> and bring back any of <FONT color=#a94407>Jeffery</FONT>'s belongings to find a clue to where he went.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-3" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Hands over Jeffery's bag)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>So, did you find anything that would tell us <FONT color=#a94407>Jeffery</FONT>'s whereabouts?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-3" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="400185" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-3-a" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Poison Skeleton had it.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>
Where did you find this?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-3-a" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="400185" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-3-b" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Do you think he became a Poison Skeleton?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>
How could an undead monster have <FONT color=#a82424>Jeffery's bag</FONT>. We have to assume Jeffery is no longer alive.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-3-b" image="QM_Gargoyle_Green.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-3-c" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>It's a real pity.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>I didn't want to say this, but I believe that's what happened. Although we don't know whether it was from a poisonous plant he ate while searching in the <FONT color=#a82424>Spirit's Grave</FONT>, or from the poisonous energy by <FONT color=#a82424>Gargoyle Nocssius</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n036_adventurer_guildmaster_gunter-3-d" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Nodding my head)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Gunther$<BR>His mother will be shocked to hear about this. Hmm, I'll take care of this, so please don't tell others about this.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
